    <section id="postingbody">
        <div class="print-information print-qrcode-container">
            <p class="print-qrcode-label">QR Code Link to This Post</p>
            <div class="print-qrcode" data-location="http://siouxfalls.craigslist.org/ret/6045580186.html"></div>
        </div>
CarHop, an industry-leader in the Buy Here, Pay Here market, has helped thousands of people with credit issues find a vehicle, improve their situation and turn their lives around. With nearly 50 locations nationwide (and growing!) we're looking for a passionate, motivated Sales Person to join our team in your area! <br>
<br>
What you can expect:<br>
- Guaranteed hourly base pay<br>
- Excellent bonus program- paid monthly!<br>
- Full health benefits (medical/dental/vision)<br>
- 401(k) w/ excellent company match<br>
- A work/life balance with a generous Paid Time Off program<br>
<br>
What we expect:<br>
- Successful sales experience<br>
- Outgoing personality with experience building rapport with customers<br>
- Ability to manage multiple priorities at one time with excellent follow-up skills<br>
- Ability to relate to &amp; communicate with excited Buyers! <br>
- We don't just sell cars &amp; credit, we truly make a difference in the lives of our customers!<br>
<br>
Two easy ways to apply:<br>
1.) Reply to this posting and attach a copy of your most current resume<br>
2.) <a href="http://www.carhop.com/careers" rel="nofollow">Apply Online Now!<br>
<br>
EOE.<br>
<br>
<br>
